{"type": "article", "id": 3708, "title": "Normann Copenhagen可调节式台灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-20T07:43:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060523282489ulYDAUei5QyKVh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t德国设计二人组 KaschKasch 日前为丹麦家居品牌 Normann Copenhagen  设计了一款名为「Cap」的可调节式台灯，设计灵感来源于意大利米兰的漫画家托尼·巴戈特创作的漫画形象 Calimero，它是一只头上戴着蛋壳的乌黑的小鸡。KaschKasch 为这款台灯设计了一个大大的半圆形帽子，恰似 Calimero 头上的蛋壳，聚集在“帽子”下方的直射光源非常适合于作为阅读灯，呈现出雕塑一般的几何美感。定价 480 美元，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/products/cap-tablelamp?v=505042\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052328226RxYif4QwqeTvIgO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.521875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232823lNsPSTV4ohZCFQpI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232823jZmQYaGo9SU5k3WL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232823S3miBsc7OFWNXfkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}